!! Introduction
See if you find the Word Trinity in the Bible. You will find no results. We are looking at God's Triune nature. We are looking at the fact that God is in nature.

Throughout history we have an artist's attempt to capture an idea.

As we look at the idea of God's Triune nature, what we understand is that when we consider the Word of God, not every word that we explain that nature or attribute has to appear in the Bible. As we are studying this today, bear in mind with this statement:

